    "spell": {
        "name": "Capital Dividend",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Through diet and other strict regimens, you\u2019ve fortified your body as Kalistrade\u2019s teachings have fortified your mind. You remain at 1 Hit Point, and your skin takes on a slight warm glow.   \n  \nFor the next minute, any time you would regain Hit Points from a healing effect, this magic amplifies the effect, and you regain an additional 8 Hit Points.",
